<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .menu-item {
            display: flex;
            margin: 20px;
        }

        .item-image img {
            max-width: 20px;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        .item-description {
            flex: 1;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Our Restaurant Menu</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="menu-item">
        <div class="item-image">
            <img src="~/Content/images/chicken-biryani.jpg" alt="Item 1">
        </div>
        <div class="item-description">
            <h2>Item 1</h2>
            <p>Chicken biryani is a flavorful Indian dish that combines tender chicken pieces,
            fragrant basmati rice, and a blend of aromatic spices. It's cooked with onions, tomatoes, and yogurt, creating a delicious 
            and savory one-pot meal. 
            Garnished with fresh herbs and fried onions, it's a true culinary delight.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="menu-item">
        <div class="item-image">
            <img src="~/Content/images/Panner butter Masala.jpg" alt="Item 2">
        </div>
        <div class="item-description">
            <h2>Item 2</h2>
            <p>Paneer butter masala is a popular Indian vegetarian dish made with cubes of paneer (Indian cottage cheese) 
            cooked in a rich and creamy tomato-based gravy, flavored with butter and a blend of aromatic spices. 
            It's known for its luscious, mildly spiced, and slightly sweet flavor..</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>
